#: data/portals.metainfo.xml.in:11
msgid "Access system features in a secure way"
msgstr "Accediu a les funcions del sistema d'una manera segura"

#: data/portals.metainfo.xml.in:13
msgid ""
"Portals provide APIs to secure apps which enable them to access system "
"features while requiring informed consent."
msgstr ""
"Els Portals proporcionen API per assegurar les aplicacions que permeten "
"accedir a les funcions del sistema i que requereixen un consentiment "
"informat."

